SUMMARY:How Deep Is Your Love | In Light Human Rights Documentary Film Fe
 stival
DESCRIPTION:In How Deep Is Your Love\, marine biologists venture into Ear
 th's last wilderness—the deep sea—to study "alien-like" creatures and
  ancient ecosystems thriving in darkness. As they race to map undiscovere
 d species\, the film reveals the urgent threat of deep-sea mining\, poise
 d to devastate these fragile habitats. Blending awe-inspiring exploration
  with a call to action\, it questions humanity's commitment to preserving
  an unseen and mysterious world. [101 min\; documentary\; English]
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  In <i>How Deep Is Your Love</i>\, marin
 e biologists venture into Earth's last wilderness—the deep sea—to stu
 dy "alien-like" creatures and ancient ecosystems thriving in darkness. As
  they race to map undiscovered species\, the film reveals the urgent thre
 at of deep-sea mining\, poised to devastate these fragile habitats. Blend
 ing awe-inspiring exploration with a call to action\, it questions humani
 ty's commitment to preserving an unseen and mysterious world. [101 min\; 
 documentary\; English]</p>
