SUMMARY:Another Body w/Q&A | New Americas Cinema
DESCRIPTION:Taylor\, a college student\, searches for answers and justice
  after she discovers pornographic deepfakes of herself circulating online
 . Through candid video diaries\, synthetic media\, and 2D and 3D animatio
 n\, the film takes you into Taylor's online and offline worlds\, humanizi
 ng a vast social issue with little legal recourse in this compelling and 
 urgent story of technology run rampant. [80 min\; documentary\; English]A
  Q&amp\;A will follow the screening.
