 tion and loses his mind. <i>Contains substance use.</i></p><p>  &#160\;</
 p><p><strong>Allure</strong> (10 min) | Directed by Dylan Dankel</p><p>  
 Following an onstage meltdown\, one<br />  young guitarist must confront 
 his bandmates as they demand answers\, all the while contemplating his re
 lationship with each of them. <i>Contains substance use.</i></p><p>  &#16
 0\;</p><p><strong>Just Penelope Band Doc</strong> (7 min) | Directed by B
 etzabeth Leija-Castaneda</p><p>  Through rehearsals and live sets\, this 
