SUMMARY:Belle de Jour | City Lights Film Series
DESCRIPTION:A bourgeois Parisian housewife takes on the day job of high-c
 lass prostitute as a means of coming to terms with a past trauma\, and re
 claims her personal agency and sexuality in the process. Featuring iconic
  costumes by Yves Saint Laurent\, Luis Buñuel's classic erotic drama mak
 es surrealism sexy. [101 min\; drama\; French with English subtitles]
