 lowing the films.</strong></i></p><p><i><strong>We are Earth</strong></i>
 <strong>(dir. Zoe Rose\, 2022\, France):</strong> In a world crushed by p
 ollution\, conflicts\, eco anxiety\, alienation of the individual\, and f
