 ens of artists and designers\, this film uncovers the role of soil in the
  life of our planet and the way we as humans connect with the natural wor
 ld. From the microscopic\, to the mountain-sized\, we unpack the life cyc
 le of soil across the world and how we can reconnect with the ground that
  sustains us. [16 min\; English]</p><p><i><strong>Our Circle in the Storm
