SUMMARY:Doctor Zhivago | City Lights Film Series
DESCRIPTION:David Lean's 1965 epic Doctor Zhivago follows poet-physician 
 Yuri Zhivago (Omar Sharif) through World War I and the Russian Revolution
  as his loyalty to his wife\, Tonya (Geraldine Chaplin)\, collides with h
 is ardent bond with Lara (Julie Christie). The film won five Academy Awar
 ds\, including Cinematography and Score\, and five Golden Globes\, includ
 ing Best Motion Picture - Drama and Best Director. [197 min\; drama\; Eng
 lish]
